  • Constructor Details

    • Enemy

      public Enemy(String name, String type, int maxHp, int level)
      Primary Enemy constructor method (Type: Enemy).

      Constructs a regular enemy; one which doesn't have any story/combat text and doesn't drop any items upon defeat.

      Parameters:
      name - Enemy name
      type - Boss type
      maxHp - Enemy max hp
      level - Enemy level

    • Enemy

      public Enemy(String name, String type, int maxHp, int level, String before, String after, Item item)
      Secondary enemy constructor (Type: Boss).

      Constructs a Boss enemy which has pre and post-combat story text and drops item upon defeat.

      Parameters:
      name - Enemy name
      type - Boss type
      maxHp - Enemy max hp
      level - Enemy level
      before - Before combat story
      after - Post combat story
      item - Item dropped by enemy
